## Overview

Vendor SDK wrapper interface that provides a consistent abstraction over a
vendor-provided library or SDK. Supports loading the library, connecting to
instruments, calling SDK functions, and managing properties.

## Usage

```python
from {{ interface_name }}_interface import {{ interface_name | pascal_case }}Interface

interface = {{ interface_name | pascal_case }}Interface(library_path="/opt/vendor/lib")
interface.load_library()
interface.connect()

# Call SDK functions
result = interface.call_function("measure", channel=1)

# Read/write properties
temperature = interface.get_property("temperature")
interface.set_property("mode", "auto")

interface.disconnect()
```

